Package killdrluckygame

Class DrLuckySpace

java.lang.Object
killdrluckygame.DrLuckySpace
All Implemented Interfaces:
Space
public class DrLuckySpace extends Object implements Space
The DrLuckySpace class represents a space in the game world. It implements the Space interface and provides methods to access and manipulate the properties of the space. Each space has a unique name, position coordinates, and contains items if alloted to the space.
